version 1.0.0, 2026-05-05
- Added hybrid tolerance comparison functions (haeq, hsne, hslt, hale, hsgt, hage).
  Formula: |a - b| <= atol + rtol * max(|a|, |b|)
  Supports default (no-arg) and explicit (atol, rtol) variants for sp, dp, qp.
- Added hybrid tolerance operators: .haeq., .hsne., .hslt., .hale., .hsgt., .hage.
- Added CMakePresets.json with configure/build/test presets for GNU (gfortran) and Intel LLVM (ifx).
- Restructured as an installable CMake package with approxConfig.cmake and version file.
- Updated README with full API reference and build instructions.

